major_odu.name: Eji Ogbe
major_odu.pattern: I I I I I I I I

major_odu.modern_application: In contemporary life, Eji Ogbe teaches us to apply ancient wisdom to modern challenges. Its guidance helps navigate current situations with spiritual insight and traditional understanding.
